ergy meters, batteries, sponge iron, and solar panels, as well as surface mount technology; and LED bulbs and lights. In addition, the company provides moulding, plastic moulds, moulds and tools, painted parts, and laser marking. Jay Ushin Limited was incorporated in 1986 and is based in New Delhi, India. Jay Ushin Limited operates as a subsidiary of MINEBEA MITSUMI Inc."}}